description: A joke about an emotional cabbage in the fridge.
title: Emotional Cabbage
n_1: Charlie and Sam were in the kitchen.
c1_1: As a kid, I saw a crying vegetable in the fridge.
n_2: Charlie looked at Sam with a serious expression.
c1_2: Turns out, I had emotional cabbage.
n_4: They continued to prepare their meal, still chuckling.
